room_title: Escape room "The Vampire’s Lair" by Escape Boardman in Warren
room_description: Hearing of this recent vampire activity, you and your thrill-seeking friends travel to Transylvania in hopes of capturing video footage. While filming at Bran Castle, you discover that some of your friends are missing. You think you know where they are! As dusk approaches, you have 60 minutes to find them and kill the vampire or your fate awaits you…
